The Linux Kernel Mentorship program - open for all undergraduates: Its a 12 week paid menteeship under which students work with mentors on certain projects. Please check the Fall 2020 Linux Kernel Mentorship Program and get started. This is a remote opportunity and there is no need to relocate or move to participate.

